    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'mint condition.' This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a flawless finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further enhanced by a multi-stage paint correction and a premium ceramic coating for a deep, mirror-like shine. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, the carpets are pristine under original factory protectors, and every electronic feature operates with precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive binder of every service record performed exclusively by master technicians at the authorized dealership. With remarkably low mileage and a history of gentle, fair-weather-only use, this car offers the rare opportunity to own a modern classic in its peak form. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fit breathable car cover.",
